  "uvp_notes": "7A version ~€184, 14A version ~€189 (techgrow.nl list price). Temperature probe sensor included; no separate sensor purchase needed.",
  "notes": "Available in 7A (fuse 8A, triac 12A) and 14A (fuse 15A, triac 24A) variants; 14A row specs used for electrical figures. Controls up to 2 AC fans via triac speed control. Temperature probe (4.5m cable) included — uses proprietary probe type, not UTP. No humidity sensing or control. No day/night detection. Rotary knobs for temp setpoint (10–45°C) and hysteresis (1–7°C). Spare fuse included."
